videos.description: Trevor Booker uses a mop to dislodge the ball after it gets stuck on top of the basket. By the look on Booker's face, he was quite happy the ball still went in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA One-Play (Mop drains a two, Booker with the assist) 2015/11/18 ESHEET
